snippet.title: 50 Cent Bullies Autistic Teen on Video

localized.description:
50 Cent has come under fire for shaming a boy with autism. While traveling through the Cincinnati/Northern Kentucky International Airport 50 harassed 19-year-old Andrew Farrell of being high on drugs. 50 Cent said on his Twitter video, “Look at him. What kinds of shit you think he took before he came to work today? He high as a mother fucker right here in the airport.” Andrew, who has struggled with social anxiety and mild autism’s all his life, is very happy with the person he is and has received wide support from hundreds on social media sites since posting about the incident. 50 Cent has yet to make a public comment about the video. Nik Zecevic and Margaret J. Howell take a closer look at the incident on the Lip News.
